msgctxt "164_Akiyama"
msgid "Okay. Let's get started."
msgstr "Bien. Empecemos."

msgctxt "176_キャバ育名前"
msgid "Okay."
msgstr "Está bien."

msgctxt "188_Akiyama"
msgid "First, let's get you changed into an outfit that brings out the best of your natural beauty. Don't worry, I guarantee you'll look great."
msgstr "Primero, vamos a cambiarte a un atuendo que resalte lo mejor de tu belleza natural. No te preocupes, te garantizo que te verás genial."

msgctxt "224_Akiyama"
msgid "Not bad."
msgstr "Nada mal."

msgctxt "236_キャバ育名前"
msgid "Really? This is a little embarrassing..."
msgstr "Really? This is a little embarrassing..."

msgctxt "248_Akiyama"
msgid "It's time to go out on the club floor. Don't worry. I'm sure you'll get customers."
msgstr "Es hora de que salgas. No te preocupes. Estoy seguro de que conseguirás clientes."

msgctxt "260_キャバ育名前"
msgid "Okay..."
msgstr "Bueno..."

msgctxt "296_Akiyama"
msgid "%s, huh? That works. You'll use that name at the club from now on."
msgstr "%s, huh? That works. You'll use that name at the club from now on."

msgctxt "308_キャバ育名前"
msgid "All right. Thank you."
msgstr "All right. Thank you."

msgctxt "320_Akiyama"
msgid "First, let's get you changed into an outfit that brings out the best of your natural beauty. Don't worry, I guarantee you'll look great."
msgstr "Primero, vamos a cambiarte a un atuendo que resalte lo mejor de tu belleza natural. No te preocupes, te garantizo que te verás genial."

msgctxt "344_Akiyama"
msgid "Welcome to Elise. We're going to make you into this club's number one hostess."
msgstr "Welcome to Elise. We're going to make you into this club's number one hostess."

msgctxt "356_Akiyama"
msgid "You'll need to come up with a name to use in the club. What would you like your name to be?"
msgstr "You'll need to come up with a name to use in the club. What would you like your name to be?"

msgctxt "428_Akiyama"
msgid "I'm not quite sure how to pronounce that... Why don't we\\r\n"\n"come up with something a bit more natural?"
msgstr "I'm not quite sure how to pronounce that... Why don't we\\r\n"\n"come up with something a bit more natural?"

msgctxt "488_キャバ育名前"
msgid "Sorry, I should've called if I was going to skip work..."
msgstr "Sorry, I should've called if I was going to skip work..."

msgctxt "500_Akiyama"
msgid "It's okay. I haven't been the best manager, either.\\r\n"\n"I'll be sure to do a better job from now on."
msgstr "It's okay. I haven't been the best manager, either.\\r\n"\n"I'll be sure to do a better job from now on."

msgctxt "512_キャバ育名前"
msgid "Okay."
msgstr "Está bien."

msgctxt "548_Akiyama"
msgid "You're doing well. Are you settling in to your new life yet?"
msgstr "You're doing well. Are you settling in to your new life yet?"

msgctxt "560_キャバ育名前"
msgid "Yes! I love my apartment. I could spend a whole day there and not get bored or homesick!"
msgstr "Yes! I love my apartment. I could spend a whole day there and not get bored or homesick!"

msgctxt "572_Akiyama"
msgid "I'm glad to hear that, but don't forget to call home now and then."
msgstr "I'm glad to hear that, but don't forget to call home now and then."

msgctxt "584_キャバ育名前"
msgid "What!? No! I don't wanna have anything to do with my father anymore! I don't even wanna hear his voice!"
msgstr "What!? No! I don't wanna have anything to do with my father anymore! I don't even wanna hear his voice!"

msgctxt "596_Akiyama"
msgid "Aren't your parents paying for your tuition? If you really wanted to cut ties with them, you'd have to quit school."
msgstr "Aren't your parents paying for your tuition? If you really wanted to cut ties with them, you'd have to quit school."

msgctxt "608_キャバ育名前"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "620_Akiyama"
msgid "(Sounds like a tough situation. Nothing I can really do to help it, though.)"
msgstr "(Sounds like a tough situation. Nothing I can really do to help it, though.)"

